                                                                    :hasTransformativeWork :Elementary ;
                                                                    :sourceElement :Observation_and_Deduction ;
                                                                    :targetElement :Observation_and_Deduction ;
                                                                    :rationale "Holmes's signature method of observation and deduction is reused as the recognizable prototype of the protagonist's function." ;
                                                                    rdfs:label "Op_Canon_of_Sherlock_Holmes_to_Elementary_DeductiveMethodImitation" .


###  http://example.org/palimpsests#Op_Canon_of_Sherlock_Holmes_to_Elementary_HolmesAddictionArc
