                                                                  rdfs:label "Op_Canon_of_Sherlock_Holmes_to_Sherlock_CharacterIntensification" .


###  http://example.org/palimpsests#Op_Canon_of_Sherlock_Holmes_to_Sherlock_CrossMediaTransformation
