                                                                    rdfs:label "Op_Romeo_and_Juliet_to_West_Side_Story_RelationTopologyInheritance" .


###  http://example.org/palimpsests#Op_Romeo_and_Juliet_to_West_Side_Story_SettingTransposition
:Op_Romeo_and_Juliet_to_West_Side_Story_SettingTransposition rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
