                                                            :targetElement :Canon_Characters_Yun_Tianming ;
                                                            :rationale "Canonical characters such as Yun Tianming are reused to suture the continuation to the parent text." ;
                                                            rdfs:label "Op_The_Three_Body_Problem_to_ThreeBodyX_CharacterImitation" .


###  http://example.org/palimpsests#Op_The_Three_Body_Problem_to_ThreeBodyX_NarrativeGapExpansion
