                                                               :sourceElement :Yun_Tianming_Blank_Storyline ;
                                                               :targetElement :Expanded_Cosmic_Sociology ;
                                                               :rationale "As an authorized continuation, it fills a storyline the parent text left blank (Yun Tianming's fate), expanding the original's cosmic-sociology concepts into new territory." ;
                                                               rdfs:label "Op_The_Three_Body_Problem_to_ThreeBodyX_NarrativeGapExpansion" .


###  http://example.org/palimpsests#Op_The_Three_Body_Problem_to_ThreeBodyX_WorldInheritance
