                                                            :rationale "The witches of Oz are reused as the retelling's central figures." ;
                                                            rdfs:label "Op_The_Wonderful_Wizard_of_Oz_to_Wicked_CharacterImitation" .


###  http://example.org/palimpsests#Op_The_Wonderful_Wizard_of_Oz_to_Wicked_CrossMediaTransformation
:Op_The_Wonderful_Wizard_of_Oz_to_Wicked_CrossMediaTransformation rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
