###  http://example.org/palimpsests#Op_The_Wonderful_Wizard_of_Oz_to_Wicked_PerspectiveShift
:Op_The_Wonderful_Wizard_of_Oz_to_Wicked_PerspectiveShift rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
