                                                          rdfs:label "Op_The_Wonderful_Wizard_of_Oz_to_Wicked_PerspectiveShift" .


###  http://example.org/palimpsests#Op_The_Wonderful_Wizard_of_Oz_to_Wicked_VillainSubversion
:Op_The_Wonderful_Wizard_of_Oz_to_Wicked_VillainSubversion rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
